Tonight on 4 PEEPS 4 WEEKS
We covered a brief history of curtain wall And the “two cups one guy” weather proofing principle and how this applies to curtain wall and skylight systems.
•
Next week is forensic facades… how to determine facade details from photos and the web sleuthing
